commit 900239233e1a31ffbfea7d0ec04861dbfcbc3d8a
Author: Alexandros Bantis <ambantis@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Sep 2 18:51:42 2012 -0700

    Refactored object database persistence.
    
    1) instead of having connection details within a PostgresBugDAO object, the connection information is included within web.xml as context-parameters.
    2) the ContextListener now implements contextInitialized by establishing a connection and then setting that connection as a Servlet Init Parameter.
    3) com.x460dot11.Hibernator contains a public static method that takes as its argument a connection and returns an ArrayList of bugs, via a query to bugdb
    4) the com.x460dot11.servlet.ServletLogin gets the connection parameter and uses it to create an ArrayList of bugs, and then sets this array list as a session parameter.
    5) the welcome.jsp the grabs the bugs session parameter and uses a jsp:forEach loop to print out the bug ids in a table.

